                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Fît en nous passer un frisson,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Et ce frisson était dé flamme !…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Sa mélodieuse chanson",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "D'un doux émoi pénétrait l'âme !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sa mélodieuse chanson,\nD'un doux émoi pénétrait l'âme !\nNos cœurs battaient à l'unisson !\nSa mélodieuse chanson\nFît en nous passer un frisson,\nEt ce frisson était dé flamme !…\nSa mélodieuse chanson\nD'un doux émoi pénétrait l'âme !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Je pleurais sans savoir pourquoi…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Qu'elles étaient douces, mes larmes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Et Bertha pleurait comme moi ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Je pleurais… sans savoir pourquoi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
