                    "line_text": "La fauvette chantait, ma foi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Nous n'éprouvions nulles alarmes…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Mais Bertha pleurait comme moi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Qu'elles étaient douces, nos larmes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je pleurais sans savoir pourquoi…\nQu'elles étaient douces, mes larmes !\nEt Bertha pleurait comme moi ;\nJe pleurais… sans savoir pourquoi !\nLa fauvette chantait, ma foi !\nNous n'éprouvions nulles alarmes…\nMais Bertha pleurait comme moi !\nQu'elles étaient douces, nos larmes !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Sans le vouloir — dans le chemin —",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Pourtant mon trouble était extrême,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "De Bertha je saisis la main,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
